Summary:        A compiled, garbage-collected, concurrent programming language
License:        BSD-3-Clause
Group:          Development/Languages/Other
URL:            http://golang.org
Source:         http://golang.org/dl/go%{version}.src.tar.gz
Source1:        go-rpmlintrc
Source4:        README.SUSE
